#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:25
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This section provides an overview of how &kappname; handles loans. Loan "
#| "regulations and customs vary from locality to locality. For detailed "
#| "explanations of loans, as well as information on local regulations and "
#| "customs, please see other resources."
msgid ""
"This chapter describes how &kmymoney; handles loans. Loan regulations and "
"customs vary from locality to locality. For detailed explanations of loans, "
"as well as information on local regulations and customs, please see other "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"Järgnevalt antakse ülevaade, kuidsa &kappname; kohtleb laene. Laenudega "
"seotud reeglid ja tavad erinevad riigiti. Üksikasjalikke selgitusi laenude "
"ning kohalike reeglite ja tavade kohta tuleb otsida muudest allikatest."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:31
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A loan is an agreement under which a borrower receives money from a "
#| "lender and agrees to repay the money at some future date. &kappname; "
#| "allows you to track loans by which you, as borrower, borrow money from "
#| "or, as lender, lend money to someone else. Most individuals borrow more "
#| "than they lend, so you will generally be the borrower and a finance "
#| "company will generally be the lender. If you lend money to a family "
#| "member or a friend, you can use &kappname; to keep track of this loan as "
#| "well."
msgid ""
"A loan is an agreement under which a borrower receives money from a lender "
"and agrees to return the money as one or more repayments in the future. "
"&kmymoney; allows you to track loans by which you, as borrower, receive "
"money from or, as lender, give money to someone else. Most individuals "
"borrow more than they lend, so you will generally be the borrower and a "
"finance company will generally be the lender. If you lend money to a family "
"member or a friend, you can use &kmymoney; to keep track of this loan as "
"well."
msgstr ""
"Laen kujutab endast lepingut, millega laenuvõtja saab raha laenuandjalt ning "
"kohustub selle millalgi tulevikus tagasi maksma. &kappname; võimaldab "
"jälgida laene, mille puhul sa kui laenuvõtja oled laenanud kelleltki raha "
"või kui laenuandja laenanud kellelegi raha. Enamik inimesi võtab rohkem "
"laenu kui annab, nii et kõige tavalisem juhtum on see, kui sina oled "
"laenuvõtja ja rahaasutus on laenuandja. Kui aga laenad näiteks raha "
"pereliikmele või sõbrale, võid ka sellel laenul &kappname; abil silma peal "
"hoida."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This guide will assume that you are borrowing from some sort of finance "
"company, but the topics discussed here apply equally well to loans that you "
"might make to a person. The main difference between borrowing and lending "
"money is that an expense category is used to keep track of interest when "
"borrowing money and an income category is used to keep track of interest "
"when lending money."
msgstr ""
"Siin eeldataksegi, et sa oled laenanud mõnelt rahaasutuselt, kuid sama hästi "
"käib kõik siin kõneldav ka juhtumite kohta, mil oled ise kellelegi raha "
"laenanud. Laenu võtmise ja andmise peamine erinevus seisneb selles, et "
"intressi jälgimiseks kasutatakse kulukategooriat, kui oled laenu võtnud, ja "
"tulukategooriat, kui oled laenu andnud."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some relevant terms"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:50
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Loan Principal"
msgid "Principal"
msgstr "Laenu põhisumma"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:51
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The amount that is lent out is called the <quote>loan amount</quote> or "
#| "<quote>principal</quote>."
msgid ""
"The amount that is borrowed is called the <quote>principal</quote> or "
"<quote>loan amount</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Välja laenatud summat nimetatakse <quote>laenusummaks</quote> või "
"<quote>põhisummaks</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Term"
msgstr "Kestus"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:58
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The period of a loan is called its <quote>term</quote> of the loan. At "
#| "the end of the term, the entirety of the principal will have been "
#| "returned to the borrower. Terms are generally expressed in weeks, months, "
#| "or years. A term can also be expressed by the number of payments. For "
#| "example, a one year loan with weekly repayments could be described as a "
#| "one year loan or a loan with 52 repayments."
msgid ""
"The period or duration of a loan is called the <quote>term</quote> of the "
"loan. At the end of the term, the entirety of the principal will have been "
"returned to the lender. Terms are generally expressed in weeks, months, or "
"years. A term can also be expressed by the number of payments. For example, "
"a one year loan with weekly repayments could be described as a one year loan "
"or a loan with 52 repayments."
msgstr ""
"Laenuperioodi nimetatakse <quote>kestuseks</quote>. Selle lõpuks peab kogu "
"põhisumma olema laenuandjale tagastatud. Tavaliselt on kestuseks nädalad, "
"kuud või aastad. Kestust saab siiski väljendada ka maksete arvuna. Näiteks "
"üheaastast laenu iganädalate tagasimaksetega võib sama hästi nimetada "
"üheaastaseks laenuks või 52 tagasimaksega laenuks."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Repayments"
msgstr "Tagasimaksed"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The repayment of the principal to the lender is generally not done as a "
#| "lump sum. Instead, a series of repayments are made, each representing a "
#| "portion of the principal. Such repayments are sometimes known as "
#| "<quote>amortization payments</quote> and in &kappname; "
#| "<quote>Amortization</quote> is defined as the act of paying off a loan in "
#| "installments."
msgid ""
"The repayment of the principal to the lender is generally not done as a lump "
"sum. Instead, a series of repayments are made, each representing a portion "
"of the principal. Such repayments are sometimes known as <quote>amortization "
"payments</quote> and in &kmymoney; <quote>Amortization</quote> is defined as "
"the act of paying off a loan in installments."
msgstr ""
"Laenu põhisummat ei maksta laenuandjale tavaliselt tagasi tervikuna. Selle "
"asemel tehakse mitu tagasimakset, millest igaüks vastab kindlale osale "
"põhisummast. Mõnijkord nimetatakse niisuguseid tagasimakseid "
"<quote>amortisatsioonimakseteks</quote> ning &kappname;s ongi "
"<quote>amortisatsioon</quote> määratletud laenu tagasimaksmisena osade kaupa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment Frequency"
msgstr "Maksete sagedus"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The frequency of installments is referred to as <quote>Payment Frequency</"
#| "quote> in &kappname;. Examples of period might be weekly, bi-weekly, "
#| "monthly, quarterly, or yearly. In the US, periodic payments are most "
#| "commonly made every month, therefore the loan's period is one month."
msgid ""
"The frequency of installments is referred to as <quote>Payment Frequency</"
"quote>. Examples of this might be weekly, bi-weekly, monthly, quarterly, or "
"yearly. This is also sometimes referred to as the payment period. In the US, "
"periodic payments are most commonly made every month, therefore the loan's "
"period is one month."
msgstr ""
"Osamaksete sagedust nimetatakse &kappname;s <quote>maksete sageduseks</"
"quote>. Perioodiks võib olla kord nädalas, kahe nädala tagant, kuus, "
"kvartalis või aastas. USAs tehakse perioodilisi makseid kõige sagedamini "
"kord kuus, niisiis laenuperiood on üks kuu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interest Rate"
msgstr "Intressimäär"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the privilege of being able to use the money, the borrower will pay the "
"lender a fee called the <quote>interest</quote>, normally expressed as a "
"percentage of the amount of the principal over a defined period. Interest "
"rates can be fixed, where the interest rate does not change over the "
"lifetime of the loan, or variable, where the interest rate can change over "
"time. Typically, interest payments are included with each periodic repayment."
msgstr ""
"Luksuse eest kasutada raha maksab laenuvõtja laenuandjale tasu, mida "
"nimetatakse <quote>intressiks</quote> ja mida tavaliselt väljendatakse "
"protsendina põhisumma kogusest kindla ajavahemiku jooksul. Intressimäär võib "
"olla fikseeritud, millisel juhul see laenu kestuse ajal ei muutu, või "
"muutuv, millisel juhul see ajas muutub. Tüüpiliselt hõlmavad perioodilised "
"maksed ka intressimakseid."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that a loan in &kmymoney; must have an interest rate greater than 0. "
"Money borrowed or lent with no interest must be entered as a liability or "
"asset account."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Periodic Repayments"
msgstr "Perioodilised tagasimaksed"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:103
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Since these repayments are generally made on some sort of scheduled "
#| "basis, such as weekly, monthly, quarterly, or yearly, they are referred "
#| "to as <quote>periodic repayments</quote>. The sum of all periodic "
#| "repayments plus the final repayment will add up to the loan principal "
#| "plus the interest."
msgid ""
"Since repayments are generally made on some sort of scheduled basis, such as "
"weekly, monthly, quarterly, or yearly, they are referred to as "
"<quote>periodic repayments</quote>. The sum of all periodic repayments plus "
"the final repayment will add up to the loan principal plus the interest."
msgstr ""
"Kuna tagasimakseid tehakse tavaliselt kindla ajagraafiku alusel, olgu "
"perioodiks siis nädal, kuu, kvartal või aasta, nimetatakse neid "
"<quote>perioodilisteks tagasimakseteks</quote>. Kõigi perioodiliste "
"tagasimaksete summa pluss lõplik tagasimakse annabki kokku laenu põhisumma "
"pluss intressi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fees"
msgstr "Teenustasud"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There may be other fees besides interest that are required to be paid "
#| "with every installment. These are called <quote>recurring fees</quote>. "
#| "Examples of recurring fees include (but are not necessarily limited to):"
msgid ""
"There may be other fees besides interest that are required to be paid, "
"possibly with every installment. These are called <quote>recurring fees</"
"quote>. Examples of recurring fees include (but are not necessarily limited "
"to):"
msgstr ""
"Lisaks intressile võib olla ka muid tasusid, mida tuleb maksta igal "
"tagasimaksel. Neid nimetatakse <quote>korduvtasudeks</quote>. Mõned, aga "
"kaugeltki mitte kõik korduvtasude näited on järgmised:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:120
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<quote>Impound</quote> or <quote>escrow</quote> account payments. "
#| "(Payments of this sort are commonly used to hold funds to pay annual or "
#| "bi-annual property taxes.)"
msgid ""
"<quote>Impound</quote> or <quote>escrow</quote> account payments. Payments "
"of this sort are commonly used to hold funds to pay annual or bi-annual "
"property taxes."
msgstr ""
"deponeerimiskonto (inglise keelees <quote>impound</quote> või <quote>escrow</"
"quote>) maksed - seda laadi maksete eesmärk on tavaliselt koguda raha iga-"
"aastaste või igapoolaastaste kinnisvaramaksude tasumiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mortgage insurance"
msgstr "hüpoteeklaenu kindlustus"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disability insurance"
msgstr "töövõimetuskindlustus"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan account maintenance fees"
msgstr "laenukonto hooldustasu"

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Summary"
msgstr "Kokkuvõte"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:138
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In summary, the borrower receives a lump sum from the lender at the start "
#| "of the loan. The borrower makes a periodic payment to the lender. The "
#| "periodic payment is the sum of the principal payment (which is used to "
#| "pay down the balance of the loan) plus the interest payment (which "
#| "rewards the lender for allowing the use of the money by the borrower) "
#| "plus any recurring fees (which cover any incidentals.) At the end of the "
#| "loan, the borrower has paid back the entire principal."
msgid ""
"In summary, the borrower receives a lump sum from the lender at the start of "
"the loan. The borrower makes a periodic payment to the lender. The amount of "
"the periodic payment is the sum of the principal payment (which is used to "
"pay down the balance or remaining principal of the loan,) the interest "
"payment (which rewards the lender for allowing the use of the money by the "
"borrower,) plus any recurring fees (which cover any incidentals.) At the end "
"of the loan, the borrower has paid back the entire principal."
msgstr ""
"Kokkuvõtteks võib öelda, et laenuvõtja saab laenu alguses laenuandjalt "
"terviksumma. Laenuvõtja teeb laenuandjale perioodilisi makseid. Perioodiline "
"makse koosneb põhisumma maksest (millega kahandatakse laenubilanssi) ja "
"intressimaksest (mis on lisatasu laenuandjale võimaluse tagamise eest "
"laenuvõtjal raha kasutada) ning vastavalt tingimustele ka korduvtasudest. "
"Laenutähtaja lõouks peab laenuvõtja olema tagasi maksnud kogu põhisumma."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Näide"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:151
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For an example, you might borrow $25,000.00 for a new auto and agree to "
#| "pay the bank one payment each month for 60 months. The interest rate on "
#| "the loan might be 5.5%."
msgid ""
"For an example, you might borrow $25,000.00 for a new automobile and agree "
"to pay the bank one payment each month for 60 months. The interest rate on "
"the loan might be 5.5% per year."
msgstr ""
"Oletame näiteks, et laenad 25 000 dollarit uue auto ostmiseks ja nõustud "
"pangale tagasi maksma üks kord kuus järgmise 60 kuu jooksul, Laenu "
"intressimäär on, ütleme, 5,5%."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:157
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In this scenario, the loan amount is $25,000.00. The term of the loan is "
#| "60 months or 5 years. The term of the loan could also be described as 60 "
#| "payments since there will be one payment per month for 5 years. The "
#| "repayment frequency is one month since periodic repayments will be made "
#| "once a month. The periodic repayment, which is calculated by &kappname;, "
#| "would be $477.53."
msgid ""
"In this scenario, the loan amount is $25,000.00. The term of the loan is 60 "
"months or 5 years. The term of the loan could also be described as 60 "
"payments since there will be one payment per month for 5 years. The "
"repayment frequency is one month since periodic repayments will be made once "
"a month. The periodic repayment, which is calculated by &kmymoney;, would be "
"$477.53."
msgstr ""
"Sel juhul on laenu kogus 25 000 dollarit. Laenu kestus on 60 kuud ehk 5 "
"aastat. Laenu võib nimetada ka 60 makse laenuks, sest seda tuleb tagasi "
"maksta üks kord kuus viie aasta jooksul. Maksete sagedus on kord kuus, sest "
"perioodilisi tagasimakseid tehakse üks kord muus. Perioodiline tagasimakse, "
"mille arvutab välja juba &kappname;, oleks sellisel juhul 477,53 dollarit."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <quote>loan schedule</quote> is a chart or table that shows the date that "
"a repayment should be made and the amount of each periodic repayment. Often, "
"these schedules break the periodic payment down into its constituent parts: "
"the principal repayment, the interest payment, and the recurring fees "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Laenu ajaplaan</quote> kujutab endast diagrammi või tabelit, mis "
"näitab kuupäevi, mil tuleb teha tagasimaksed, ja iga perioodilise "
"tagasimakse summat. Sageli liigendavad sellised ajaplaanid perioodilise "
"tagasimakse koostisosadeks: põhisumma tagasimakse, intressimakse ja "
"korduvtasude makse."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a New Loan"
msgstr "Uue laenu loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In &kappname;, a loan is a type of account. Therefore, to create a new "
#| "loan, you begin by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Account</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>New Account</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Continue by "
#| "answering the questions that the wizard poses to you."
msgid ""
"In &kmymoney;, a loan is a type of account. Therefore, to create a new loan, "
"you begin by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Account</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New Account</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. "
"Continue by answering the questions that the wizard poses to you."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;s kujutab laen endast kontotüüpi. Seepärast vali uue laenu "
"loomiseks menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Konto</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uus "
"konto</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vasta küsimustele, mida ilmuv nõustaja "
"sulle esitab."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>New Account Setup</guilabel> wizard not only sets up a Loan "
"Account, but also creates a <guilabel>Scheduled Transaction</guilabel> for "
"the periodic payments. If you try to edit either the Loan Account or the "
"associated Scheduled Transaction, you will be presented with the "
"<guilabel>Edit Loan Account Wizard</guilabel>. This allows you to adjust "
"many of the details of the loans, but not all. Unfortunately, some aspects "
"of the Loan Account cannot currently be changed, such as the account's "
"parent account."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you display the <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Schedules View</"
"link>, right-click on any of the listed schedules, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Edit scheduled transaction</guimenuitem> from the menu which "
"pops up, &kmymoney; will display the <guilabel>Edit scheduled transaction</"
"guilabel> dialog. In contrast, if you do this with a loan schedule, you will "
"be shown the <guilabel>Edit Loan Account Wizard</guilabel>, and mentioned "
"above. However, if you hold down the <keycap>&Shift;</keycap> key when you "
"click <guimenuitem>Edit scheduled transaction</guimenuitem>, the "
"<guilabel>Edit scheduled transaction</guilabel> dialog for the loan will be "
"show, where you can change some of the details of the recurring transaction."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also note that if you delete the schedule associated with a loan, you cannot "
"undo this action, and will have to start from scratch, creating a new loan "
"account and schedule."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Optionally, a loan can be associated with a particular institution. If "
#| "you are borrowing from a mortgage company or a car loan company, you "
#| "could create an institution entry that describes this firm and associate "
#| "the institution with your loan. If you are borrowing from your Uncle Ted, "
#| "there is no requirement to set up an institution."
msgid ""
"Optionally, as with any other account, a loan can be associated with a "
"particular institution. If you are borrowing from a mortgage company or a "
"car loan company, you could create an institution that describes this firm "
"and associate your loan with the institution. If you are borrowing from your "
"Uncle Ted, there is no need to set up an institution."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks võib laenu seostada konkreetse rahaasutusega. Kui võtad laenu "
"hüpoteegiettevõttelt või autolaenuettevõttelt, võid luua rahaasutuse, mis "
"kirjeldab seda ettevõtet ja seostab selle sinu laenuga. Kui laenad onu Miku "
"käest, ei ole rahaasutuse loomine sugugi vajalik."

#. Tag: title
#: details-loans.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Making Extra Principle Repayments On Loans"
msgstr "Laenu põhisumma lisatagasimaksete tegemine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to make an extra principal repayment, you can do so. "
"Simply <link linkend=\"details.ledger.transactions\">enter a transaction</"
"link> using the ledger. This extra repayment of principal will be taken into "
"account for the interest calculation that happens for the next periodic "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid põhisummat ennaktempos tagasi maksta, on ka see täiesti võimalik. "
"Selleks lihtsalt <link linkend=\"details.ledger.transactions\">sisesta "
"tehing</link> pearaamatus. Põhisumma täiendavat tagasimakset arvestatakse "
"intressi arvutamisel järgmise perioodilise makse jaoks."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Examples of extra principal payments include (but are not necessarily "
"limited to):"
msgstr ""
"Mõned, aga sugugi mitte kõik näited põhisumma täiendavate tagasimaksete "
"kohta:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contributing an extra $50 a month"
msgstr "kuus täiendava 50 dollari eraldamine."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Doubling the periodic principal repayment for every period. (The principal "
"repayment can be found for any particular period by referring to the loan "
"schedule.)"
msgstr ""
"iga perioodi perioodilise põhisumma tagasimakse kahekordistamine (põhisumma "
"tagasimakse suuruse igal perioodil võib leida laenu ajaplaanist)."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Making a 13th principal repayment every year. (This assumes a loan that is "
"repaid in monthly installments.)"
msgstr ""
"igal aastal põhisumma 13. tagasimakse sooritamine (eelduseks on laenu "
"tagasimaksmine kuukaupa)."

#. Tag: para
#: details-loans.docbook:256
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note: If you are doubling the principal repaid with every periodic "
#| "payment, you will need to recalculate the loan schedule for each "
#| "installment. This will allow there to be an accurate value for the "
#| "required principal repayment with each installment."
msgid ""
"If you are doubling the principal repaid with every periodic payment, you "
"will need to recalculate the loan schedule for each installment. This will "
"allow there to be an accurate value for the required principal repayment "
"with each installment."
msgstr ""
"Märkus: kui kahekordistad iga perioodilise makse tagasi makstava põhisumma "
"osa, tuleb iga makse korral laenu ajaplaan uuesti välja arvutada. See "
"võimaldab näha seal iga tagasimakse korral nõutava põhisumma tagasimakse "
"õiget ja täpset suurust."

